column1: 71 athletes from 6 states entered this year's meet!

Results are now official as all seven lifters passed the urinalysis performed by Redwood Toxicology - Trevor Hogans, Pat Shannon, Ken Jubas, CJ Gathagan, Curtis Miller, Nicholas Mercurio, Daniel Carinci.
1st Place - Joe's Gym of Erie, PA - 37 points
2nd Place - Schrec's Gym of Sarver, PA - 28 points
3rd Place - Camp Green Lake of Hinckley, OH - 16 points
Number of lifters in the powerlifting division: 52
Number of lifters in the bench division: 24
Number of lifters in the strict curl division: 15
